channel.title: Can't Decide
channel.description:
Well, Recently i have been trying to decide what to do for a Tutorial for everyone. I had a few options in mind, Like:
How to make a Command Generator How to make a Duel Arena, Complete with duels of-course
And a few more options, But i can't decide, I want something that people won't flame me about Copy and Paste, Well wanna be mods flame me anyway, I can deal with them, But like the hole community flaming me, That makes me feal dumb.
So i left it in your hands to decide, What should i post a tutorial on.
[b] It doesn't haft to be on one of the above, It could be something your having trouble with, And you think the community needs help with it to, It could be something you feal the community needs, So forth [/b]
So if you post something on what my next tutorial could be, I would really appreciate it.
